This may be a deterant to senseless killings, and alot cheaper than 50K a year keeping them locked up for the rest of their lives. 50k x 40 years = 2 million dollars. I don't know about you but I get 28% taken right off the top from my paycheck then 10% on every bit I spend after that, and I can think of alot better ways to spend 2 million like feeding the hungry or housing the homeless.( in America damn the third world nations. We have enough starving right here at home.)<br>
<br>
Back in midevil times they would bring scumbags like this to the town commons and tie horses to their 4 appendages and have the horses run off to the 4 corners of the world leaving the bloody torso to bleed to death. Drawn and quartered in public did wonders for the would be idiots in the crowd back then. <br>
<br>
Or better yet, turn them loose in an open courtyard with nowhere to hide. Let them stay there 24/7 for a couple of weeks and then peg them off one at a time with a single shot to the head.<br>
<br>
Essentially, do to them what they did to others so that the next dumbass out there sees what they are in for if they try this sort of thing. Hiding it behind closed doors and painlessly administering a seditive followed by the fatal injection does nothing. If you don't believe me turn on your local news... <p><table align=center>
