Inform yourself.  America is seen as this big haven of people who support capital punishment... did you know that only 26 people were executed last year?  That's right, 26.  Total.  In the entire country.<br>
<br>
I'm glad you like to spend your tax dollars making sure murderers, rapists, and thieves have air conditioning and cable TV.  I'd rather spend mine making sure children are educated, my nation is protected, and my life expectancy is long.<br>
