Maybe liberals should stop talking about all the neat things they'll do with tax dollars and do it instead.<br>
<br>
I don't understand a life in prison sentence.  The reason some people say capital punishment is wrong is because a person can be rehabilitated.  There is no rehabilitation in a life in prison sentence.  Basically, taxpayers give their money so they can rot in jail for the rest of their lives.  Makes absolutely no sense.  These people are a drain on society and a drain on every single person in this country.<br>
