Destroy them.  Maybe after a few generations that kind of violence and sociopathy will be bred out of the gene pool. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/bemarr.showUserPublicProfile?gid=cnjmorris>cnjmorris</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 301<br> <font color=#E9D756>(11/1/02 12:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3757.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sniper Caught?</span><hr size=1> How long does it take for someone to get through all the appeals and get sentenced to death?  I don't mean in Texas, I mean in America.<br>
