Look at the list of prisoners who we have gone to extremes in making their stay nice and comfy besides stock scammers and fraud artists you will find a third world dictator gone bad, and another prisoner who was catered to was Henry Lee Lucas. They took him out to restaurants. Do you know why yet? Inform yourself. <br>
